lead_paragraph: Kenya is monitoring health threats posed by the Zika virus ahead of the Olympic Games and it is too early to decide on its impact, Kenya's Olympic committee said on Tuesday, playing down comments that had suggested it could pull athletes out.

headline.print_headline: Kenya Says Undecided Over Olympics Threat Posed by Zika Virus
